    <description>用来捏角色外观的工具。打开编辑器，挑贴图、调图层、换颜色，改完实时就能看到效果。做好了可以直接打包成独立模组，拿去分享或者给别的存档用。

A character appearance editor. Open it, pick textures, tweak layers, adjust colors — changes show up in real time. When you're done, pack it as a standalone mod to share or reuse.
</description>
